reviews.text: Dr Lim is the best doctor ever. Patient, understanding, helpful and caring. My whole family goes to him.

Older lady at reception is very rude. Dr Lim is fantastic so will return. But hope they can train their receptionists better. They registered my name wrongly in spite of typing it from my IC. I assumed they were just mispronouncing my name like most Singaporeans do. I had to get it rectified as I needed it accurate on a referral letter. But instead of apologising when I went back to have the letter changed, the reception lady, visibly annoyed, huffed and asked me why I didn't highlight it in my earlier visit and rudely asked me to hand her my documents so she can make the changes. Its 10am and this lady is already so agitated....

Dr Lim is by far the friendliest doctor I meet! First thing enter his room he will great you with a big smile! You can even hear him greeting other patients when you are outside waiting! He told me to give him a chance to trust him before going to specialist and he get my issue fix less than a month! Thank you Dr Lim!

Dr lim is an amazing rare doc that listens and is ever so patient . He is careful and he is ever understanding to ever single whim the patient have ..  its fortunate that he see kids too .
